## Your Project Structure Should Look Like:
```
chatbot/
├── .env              ← Your secret API key (NOT in git)
├── .gitignore        ← Tells git to ignore .env (IN git)
├── .env.example      ← Template for others (IN git)
├── app.py
├── chatbot.py
├── requirements.txt
├── README.md
└── templates/
    └── index.html